| 8 | `research-assistant` | chat |
| 9 | `sql-expert` | qa |
| 10 | `summarizer` | qa |
| 11 | `task-planner` | chat |
| 12 | `translator` | qa |

## Environment Variables

| Variable | Required |
|----------|----------|
| `LYZR_API_KEY` | Yes |
| `LYZR_USER_ID` | No |
| `LYZR_ORG_ID` | No |
| `LYZR_MEMBERSTACK_TOKEN` | No |

## Storage

- `agents/` - Your deployed agent configs
- `.env` - API credentials

## Development

```bash
pip install -e ".[dev]"
pytest tests/ -v
ruff check src/
mypy src/
```

